results.deck: Runesoft GmbH was founded as e.p.i.c. interactive entertainment gmbh in Tübingen in the year 2000.
results.description:
The focus of Runesoft is to port popular computer games to alternative computer systems such as the Apple Macintosh, Linux, Amiga, MorphOS and ZETA. 
Runesoft also does the publishing and marketing for the ported games, wherever possible on a worldwide basis.
